{"tid":1076984,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"日劇「老公的陰莖插不進來」　石橋菜津美「露點＋綑綁」！","createTime":"2019-03-25T09:13:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-03T19:15:47.000Z","uid":209051,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1624fd1de1ae80dd8b26fb0862c8b4d1054a27ab","tid":1076984,"uid":209051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T09:13:29.000Z","msg":"記者詹維耕／台北報導<br />\n日本暢銷書「老公的陰莖插不進來」，本來只是作者隨筆的發表，後來大受歡迎，出版後更是成為暢銷書，看似荒謬的書名和內容，卻是作者的真實故事，最近也改編成日劇，由石橋菜津美和中村蒼主演，第一集就有18禁畫面出現，女星石橋菜津美飾演的女主角第一集就露了兩點，情節引爆網友熱議，不少書迷來留言「其實是個悲傷的故事」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach-setn-com.cdn.ampproject.org/i/s/attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/03/24/1841444-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach-setn-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fi%2Fs%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F03%2F24%2F1841444-XXL.jpg&h=4203510f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲石橋菜津美露點。（圖／翻攝畫面）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach-setn-com.cdn.ampproject.org/i/s/attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/03/24/1841445-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach-setn-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fi%2Fs%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F03%2F24%2F1841445-XXL.jpg&h=d9a61d60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作者木靈曾說:「我們花了整整四年才插進來一半，跟板塊一樣，每年僅下沉幾公分。我們的性愛，簡直是地球等級。」她與老公相識超過20年，但從交往到結婚，兩人從未順利性交，這樣的故事看似荒誕，卻引起讀者共鳴，改編日劇上檔後，卻是先以日劇少有的露點畫面，震撼觀眾視覺，引發網友熱烈討論。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach-setn-com.cdn.ampproject.org/i/s/attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/03/24/1841446-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach-setn-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fi%2Fs%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F03%2F24%2F1841446-XXL.jpg&h=ae38cf90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲書名「老公的陰莖插不進來」。（圖／翻攝畫面）<br />\n網友評論有的討論劇情，也有人重點放在露點畫面，「日劇露點..好不習慣」，「書名很勁爆 但故事很悲傷」，「越看越悲傷」，「很悲傷的故事心會揪一下」，「大A小B」，「會越看心情越低落」，「覺得日本女性都很壓抑」，「原作真的是個悲傷的故事」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www-setn-com.cdn.ampproject.org/v/s/www.setn.com/m/ampnews.aspx?amp_js_v=a2&amp;amp_gsa=1&amp;NewsID=516751&amp;usqp=mq331AQCCAE%3D#referrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com&amp;amp_tf=%E4%BE%86%E6%BA%90%EF%BC%9A%251%24s&amp;ampshare=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D516751\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww-setn-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fv%2Fs%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fampnews.aspx%3Famp_js_v%3Da2%26amp_gsa%3D1%26NewsID%3D516751%26usqp%3Dmq331AQCCAE%253D%23referrer%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.google.com%26amp_tf%3D%25E4%25BE%2586%25E6%25BA%2590%25EF%25BC%259A%25251%2524s%26ampshare%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.setn.com%252FNews.aspx%253FNewsID%253D516751&d=Peq93FhG%2BXbpjcIFBj2O6U9C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=a71d4b1b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www-setn-com.cdn.ampproject.org/v/s/www.setn.com/m/ampnews.aspx?amp_js_v=a2&amp;amp_gsa=1&amp;NewsID=516751&amp;usqp=mq331AQCCAE%3D#referrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com&amp;amp_tf=%E4%BE%86%E6%BA%90%EF%BC%9A%251%24s&amp;ampshare=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D516751</a><br />\n<br />\n日劇露點好似真係少見啲，唔知好唔好睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a54ce5341f34076a9baf3e4c02ce1612f15a3f6f","tid":1076984,"uid":206522,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T09:18:33.000Z","msg":"即係老公以外的插得進去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70bc56c89046cb31999c27ed7c1db4fa28d8e777","tid":1076984,"uid":77788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T10:32:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2c5580625b6ccab1fa56843ea25863f1e9fd165c","tid":1076984,"uid":236142,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1624fd1de1ae80dd8b26fb0862c8b4d1054a27ab","tid":1076984,"uid":209051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-